{"build_type":"library","module_name":"compile-atomic-fetch-addition-operation","package_name":"compile-atomic-fetch-addition-operation","description":"Renders an atomic_fetch_add low-op into x86-64 bytes: mov rax,[rbp+address]; mov rdx,[rbp+delta]; lock xadd [rax],rdx; mov [rbp+dest],rdx. The xadd atomically sets rdx to the prior value at the address and adds delta in place; the prior value is stored into the dest slot. All operands are local slots so no fixup is needed. Mirrors render_clone_thread_operation.","function_definitions":{"compile-atomic-fetch-addition-operation":{"return_type":"void","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"inst","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"code","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"slotmap","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c15","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":15},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c16","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":16},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c72","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":72},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c133","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":133},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c137","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":137},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c139","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":139},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c149","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":149},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"c193"